COMMAND_SETGOODBYE_NOARGUMENT:
Format: set goodbye [opsi] [teks?]

Options:
- on
- off
- image
- preview
- text [teks]

Contoh:
/set goodbye on
/set goodbye image
/set goodbye text Selamat tinggal @user!

@user = mention user
@group = nama grup saat ini
@desc = deskripsi grup saat ini
